{"tid":1638504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停止黨鐵服務代替宵禁","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T04:31:04.000Z","uid":98861,"like":407,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"abfaa908fc7b959f7390cdf7a9df1571219ea1cd","tid":1638504,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"係人都知黨鐵不嬲賺盡<br />\n<br />\n炒車撞人 咩都會好快攪掂再開服務<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日禁多日唔開禁多日早收<br />\n<br />\n仲同我講佢<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為維修要早收</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好當人on9啦</span>  車行到都會停駛唔賺錢<br />\n<br />\n仲要講緊既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">車站設備</span> <br />\n<br />\n你都開撚左成日啦 我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">邊維修邊開 黨鐵以前都你禁撚樣架啦</span><br />\n<br />\n而家夜晚唔開比我地用 <br />\n<br />\n又叫曬d車長站長番去 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打機 賭錢 打麻雀</span><br />\n<br />\n仲要每個月比多<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兩千蚊暗口費</span></span><br />\n<br />\n抵你禁多意外呀<br />\n<br />\nBtw 我唔想見到有人受傷<br />\n<br />\n[size=6］<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵你仆街死啦 dllm </span>[/size=6]"},{"pid":"da4f9a9cc639836381378f72008cc4ab74cb602d","tid":1638504,"uid":98861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"7a7625c6c36e0c565882d9a4312377d8c7885b22","tid":1638504,"uid":98861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0e28c62949d0e2e958bc2e38ef2886f05d6cbe26","tid":1638504,"uid":98861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"93c2f90f6f195508d84264e8b63487b3507a75e8","tid":1638504,"uid":98861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0898db8907f059e597d13f02bd6d47adf9290633","tid":1638504,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:37:04.000Z","msg